channel.description:
Hello guys, I am looking to start a decent private server (317).im here to look for people who have experince in coding and rs servers. The server is 70% done. But i need coders to put in new items, shops, areas , fixing some bugs. Head-Coder will be given 10% of donations and co-owner spot.!! I have got VPS so it will be 24/7 Heres What i need: [size=12pt][center]HEAD-CODER[/center] [center]Im looking for a experienced coder.Head-coder will do source and client coding. To Apply for this position you must prove that you have coded before.Must have Good coding skills.Also Notice: Head-Coder will be Given [size=10pt]Co-Owner[/size].And 10% of Donations!![/center] [center]*Javaguru*[/center]
[center][size=12pt]2 CODERS[/size] I need about coders with some good experience. *spot empty* *spot empty*[/center]
[center][size=12pt]1 ADMIN[/size] Need one good admin. *spot empty*[/center]
[center][size=12pt]3 MODS[/size] need 3 good mods *spot empty* *spot empty* *spot empty*[/center]
Heres my team So far:
[center][size=12pt]OWNERS[/size] Shoveb1 (hoster & web developer) Justin (coder & web developer) *Javaguru* (apply soon. you have to do all coding) [/center]
[center][size=12pt]ADMINS[/size] Pmg Ownz Mnwv *spot empty*[/center]
[center][size=12pt]MODS[/size] *spot empty* *spot empty* *spot empty*[/center]
Heres my info:
[center]My MSN: shoveb1@hotmail.com Forums: Tell u on MSN
It has been 8 days since i bought VPS and still server havent been Fully coded and released for Player, So i really need a good coder and a co owner to help us out!
Ty -Shove[/center]
